highlights.text: Tu Aake Dekhle by King has been on Top Songs Guwahati the longest, at 62 weeks straight.
Jakoruwa Moloya by Sannidhya Bhuyan, Aarxslan, and Mrityunjoy Kakati is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Guwahati, up 23 spots at #45.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Guwahati. Kesariya is the highest at #3.
Besharam Rang (From "Pathaan") by Vishal-Shekhar, Shilpa Rao, Caralisa Monteiro, Vishal Dadlani, Shekhar Ravjiani, and Kumaar is the highest new entry on Top Songs Guwahati at #6.
